snippet.title: IAmZamber
snippet.description:
I am Zamber. For years I have been a passionate lover of youtube and finally I want to give back. I want to share my experiences for gaming, anime, steven universe and more! I hope you will support me and can smile along with me!!!!

Check out my Patreon for Full Uncut Reactions to all your favorite animated shows!
https://www.patreon.com/IAmZamber
